rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0010
rows.name: Oh, what a magnificent system![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0020
rows.name:
Not only did you link the Ares's drive to the
White Whale 2, a nigh-impossible task in itself...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0030
rows.name: But to run them in parallel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0040
rows.name: Thereby allowing the Ares to function as it always did![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0050
rows.name: Pants off to you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0060
rows.name: Now to get back the cores from Void,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0065
rows.name: make the Ares whole and return to home base,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0070
rows.name: then we can finally leave this place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0080
rows.name: Nice and simple. Juuust the way I like 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0090
rows.name:
We've achieved a hell of a lot in
a few short weeks...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0100
rows.name: We rock![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0110
rows.name:
The credit goes to our allies, chief among them the Ma-non,
who shared much wisdom with us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0120
rows.name: Humanity could not have done this alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0130
rows.name:
You know, I'm starting to think we might
just be able to pull off a win![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0140
rows.name: In Void's "contest"...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0150
rows.name: Really?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0160
rows.name: Lin...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0170
rows.name: Now's not the time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0180
rows.name: Y-yes, right... Sorry...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0200
rows.name: I didn't mean to bring all that back up...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0210
rows.name: You are not wrong to have a wafer, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0220
rows.name: Ideally,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0230
rows.name: all living creatures big and small would not fight,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0240
rows.name:
but set their eyes on a new universe while
standing knee-to-knee.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0250
rows.name: The fact is, when Void faced us,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0260
rows.name: he didn't consider pursuing that possibility.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0270
rows.name: He can't consider it, even in theory.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0280
rows.name:
His goal is survival, at the cost of all else.
Everything and everyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0290
rows.name: No more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0300
rows.name: What a lonely way to be...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0310
rows.name: If loneliness is all he knows,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0320
rows.name:
is that why he doesn't want anyone else to
make it to the next universe...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0330
rows.name: That's why he denies us...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0340
rows.name: That's right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0350
rows.name: Hang on a sec...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0360
rows.name:
He claims he's pursued us because he wants
to know what death is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0370
rows.name:
When I thought of him as evil, did I get him wrong...?
Was I too hasty?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0380
rows.name: No, there's certainly a streak of wickedness in him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0390
rows.name: He's lonely, insatiable, and curious too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0400
rows.name: In a way, he's very pure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0410
rows.name: But if it ultimately brings him to wish harm upon us,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0415
rows.name: we should call a spade a spade.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0420
rows.name: By any name,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0430
rows.name:
his intentions are inscrutable to us,
and that's the truth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0440
rows.name: It's not like he wants to be scruted, anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0450
rows.name: He's alone, and fine with it, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0460
rows.name: Trying to suss him out might just tick him off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0470
rows.name: Although...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0480
rows.name: I doubt that he even has the capacity to get angry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0490
rows.name: I gotta say,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0495
rows.name: you really seem to get him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0500
rows.name: You trying to make me puke?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0510
rows.name: I guess our minds...might've gotten mixed together,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0520
rows.name: over there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0530
rows.name: Inside of the Rift.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0540
rows.name: Mixed?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0550
rows.name: Such a curious notion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0560
rows.name: It's the place where all consciousness flows.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0570
rows.name: Me and Void, we both made it out of there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0580
rows.name: Doesn't surprise me if things got a little...buggy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0590
rows.name: So there's a bit of each of you in the other?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0600
rows.name: Maybe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0610
rows.name: ...Though,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0620
rows.name: there's one key difference between me and him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0630
rows.name: I fight to secure us a place where we can all belong together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0640
rows.name:
And that's because of a strong passion,
something Void can never possess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0650
rows.name: It's 'cause I love you all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0660
rows.name: Never were more heroic words spoken![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0670
rows.name: Truly, pearls of wisdom cast before us swine![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0680
rows.name: Ahaha ha ha...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0690
rows.name: Thought I'd shaken the whole hero thing...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0700
rows.name: I got high hopes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0710
rows.name:
Fate doesn't lay our path out in front of us—
we make it ourselves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0720
rows.name: Real body or mimeosome, doesn't matter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0730
rows.name: Because we are feeling beings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0735
rows.name: We fight to survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0740
rows.name: ...Right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0750
rows.name: The White Whale 2 is now complete.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0760
rows.name:
Furthermore, all prospective escapees
have been relocated to NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0770
rows.name: It's been hard work, but we're at the final stage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0780
rows.name:
Embark the residents, then retrieve the cores
from Void and get going.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0790
rows.name: That's it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0800
rows.name: I'm sure you must all be feeling the strain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0810
rows.name: Stay strong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0820
rows.name: We'll be needing your services just a while longer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0830
rows.name:
That said, there's still time before the
de-mat effect reaches us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0840
rows.name: You should get some rest, but don't get lazy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0850
rows.name: At ease.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32350100_MSG0860
rows.name: Dismissed![ST:wait ]
